Provides interfaces for defining user-defined functions in Beam SQL.

    Interface Description
    AggregateFn<InputT,AccumT,OutputT>

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ScalarFn.ApplyMethod
    Annotates the single method in a ScalarFn implementation that is to be applied to SQL function arguments.

Package org.apache.beam.sdk.extensions.sql.udf Description

Provides interfaces for defining user-defined functions in Beam SQL.

The contents of this package are experimental. (They are not marked as usual because that would require a dependency on the {@code :sdks:java:core} module, which we want to avoid.)
